It was planned for Henley to be in this movie but Isla Fisher was pregnant(with her third child) when they started filming so she was unable to reprise her role as Henley. So it was written that Henley left The Eye and a new female horseman named Lula, played by Lizzy Caplan, was selected by Dylan to replace Henley.
